messages.message:
We're definitely starting to see more runs with lots of tests passing - for example https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/10113/overview?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1, https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/10110/overview?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1 and https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/10109/overview?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1, which is great. Let's continue to flag tests we're seeing fail on many PRs to test owners.

The biggest thing I see causing problems is sandbox issues still. For example, this run with tons of timeouts: https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/10115/overview?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1
i think the timeouts in the last link are caused by the deployment of crafting-aihub at that time https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05L87V014J/p1716227272546869
Let me follow up with the crafting team tomorrow morning on if their fix has been rolled out; if you see other timeout examples, let me know
This is not an issue with crafting, this is an issue caused on our side by our saas automatic deployment for crafting-aihub.test.instabase.com
